reviewText: I was a little worried to order a DVD from this seller because there were mainly reviews about books. So I took a chance and purchased a DVD from this seller. The DVD was perfect! It was brand new-just as described from the seller. There were no scratches or finger prints. And for a reasonable price too. Very satisfied.

my collection is almost complete. i watch season 2 vol 8 and it was so good. i hope they will dub the ova's and sesaon three. im counting down the days for the final vol. if anyone is looking for a good anime, pick this anime.
